scripts.build:macos: electron-packager . --overwrite --asar --out=dist --ignore='^media$' --platform=darwin --arch=x64 --icon=static/Icon.icns --app-bundle-id=com.sindresorhus.anatine --sign='Developer ID Application: Sindre Sorhus (YG56YK5RN5)' && cd dist/Anatine-darwin-x64 && zip -ryXq9 ../Anatine-osx-${npm_package_version}.zip Anatine.app

releases.body:
Some CSS fixes, especially with dark mode.

https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/compare/1.0.0...1.1.0

Some CSS fixes and new keyboard shortcuts.

**Note that because Twitter Mobile, which this app is based on, has changed a lot of the CSS lately, Dark Mode and some keyboard shortcuts are broken. I just don't have the time to keep up on the changes. Pull request welcome.**

https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/compare/0.5.1...1.0.0

## 

Homebrew Cask users can upgrade by running: `$ brew update && brew cask install anatine`

Dark mode fixes.

https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/compare/0.5.0...0.5.1

## 

Homebrew Cask users can upgrade by running: `$ brew update && brew cask install anatine`

- Hides promoted tweets. https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/commit/ceb42dcaa3a748f4623f603bfbbce88fa3b2f084
- Adds (right-click) context menu that lets you copy text/links and save images. https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/commit/44ba1eff3828cffa59245edc48d3d46dfa2e5f20
- Redesigned login screen. https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/commit/8f3bacd849d86eae88cefea625db38bc1a1baf36
- Changed keyboard shortcut for dark mode. https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/commit/33126112b6109cd72af83d7c1f5b3a3e5f6593fe

https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/compare/0.4.2...0.5.0

## 

Homebrew Cask users can upgrade by running: `$ brew update && brew cask install anatine`

Fix [CSP](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Security/CSP) being disabled by mistake. https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/commit/00113d152705735c9fc12a53e9d76f99511ab458

**We recommend upgrading as soon as possible.**

## 

Homebrew Cask users can upgrade by running:

```
$ brew update && brew cask install anatine
```
Fix window dragging on OS X. Linux and Windows users don't need to update.

- Dark mode and performance improvements.
- The menubar on Windows is hidden by default. (Press <kbd>Alt</kbd> to toggle it)
- The Anatine dark mode is now independent from the OS X dark mode.  https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/commit/8e2daf96a9c57686ba6b8ff1fb79316d842a52bd

https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/compare/0.3.0...0.4.0

##### Homebrew Cask


## 

✨ @paulmolluzzo & @danhp joined the project ✨

### Dark mode You can toggle dark mode in the `Anatine` menu or with Cmd/Ctrl D / Ctrl D. _Thanks to @paulmolluzzo & @danhp_ ✨ ### New keyboard shortcuts - New DM: m - Go to next tweet: j - Go to previous tweet: k - Page down: Ctrl d - Page up: Ctrl u - Scroll to top: g g - Scroll to bottom: G ### All changes https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine/compare/0.2.0...0.3.0 ## ##### Homebrew Cask Homebrew Cask users can upgrade by running: ``` $ brew update && brew cask install anatine ```

Added a bunch of [keyboard shortcuts](https://github.com/sindresorhus/anatine#keyboard-shortcuts) and some UI improvements.
